This is how I configure my vim environment.

If you are cloning this on a new system, you must run
the following command to get the submodules to show
up in the bundle/ directory.

  git submodule update --init

here is a nice link to learn more about submodules:
http://chrisjean.com/2009/04/20/git-submodules-adding-using-removing-and-updating/
